<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_332" id="165r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_332_r1l2">Marggraf VVılhelm von Meihſen </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_332_r1l3">Gnediger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> . Vns iſt fürbraht woꝛden . vvıe etlıche ewr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_332_r1l4">dyener vnd die ewren . dem Jacob Granetell vnd hanſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_332_r1l7"> <expan>Lyebing<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan> geſellſcheffte 
<add><ab facs="#facs_332_line_1577277877393_1422"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> burgern </ab></add> etwieuıl pars gelts bey </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_332_r1l8">Reychembach in <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> herſchaft <expan>lande<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd gepıete <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_332_r1l9">vnd das cʒu Kolmecʒ gepewtet <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . als das ewrn <expan>fürſt<ex>enlichen</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_332_r1l10">gnaden der <expan>egen<ex>an</ex>t<ex>e</ex></expan> <expan>han<ex>n</ex>s</expan> lybing vnd auch heinrich Rewter </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_332_r1l11">cʒeyger dicʒ briefs . auch wol ercʒelen werden . <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> daʒ Jr <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan>
<add><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan></add> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_332_r1l12">
<add><expan>vvıllıg<ex>en</ex></expan> dınſt <expan>vvılle<ex>n</ex></expan></add> ewr fürſtenlich gnade darʒu wenden vnd mit den ~ die </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_332_r1l13">das getan <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſchicken vnd beſtellen wöllet daʒ den ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_332_r1l14">daſſelb Jr gelt wider werde . Als wir etc das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_332_r1l16"><expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> vj̃ poſt dyoniſij </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_332" id="165r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Marggraf Wilhelm von Meihsen</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Gnediger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, uns ist fürbraht
                                                worden, wie etliche ewr dyener und die ewren dem
                                                Jacob Granetell und Hansen
                                                  <expan>Lyebing<ex>en</ex></expan> und
                                                  <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan> gesellscheffte,
                                                  <add><expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> burgern</add>,
                                                etwievil pars gelts bey Reychembach in
                                                  <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> herschaft
                                                  <expan>lande<ex>n</ex></expan> und gepiete
                                                  <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> und das czu
                                                Kolmecz gepewtet <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, als
                                                das ewrn <expan>fürst<ex>enlichen</ex></expan>
                                                gnaden der <expan>egen<ex>an</ex>t<ex>e</ex></expan>
<expan>Han<ex>n</ex>s</expan> Lybing und auch
                                                Heinrich Zewter, czeyger dicz briefs, auch wol
                                                erczelen werden. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>,
                                                daz ir <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan>
<add><expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan></add>
<add><expan>willig<ex>en</ex></expan> dinst
                                                  <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan></add> ewr
                                                fürstenlich gnade darzu wenden und mit den, die das
                                                getan <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, schicken und
                                                bestellen wöllet, daz den
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dasselb ir gelt
                                                wider werde. Als wir etc. Das
                                                  <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.
                                                  <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> vi post Dyonisii.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
